[Episode 14]

3
00:01:34,520 --> 00:01:35,320
I heard

4
00:01:35,600 --> 00:01:37,320
the Empress Dowager is seeking candidates

5
00:01:37,320 --> 00:01:38,979
to select a concubine for you.

6
00:01:40,360 --> 00:01:41,910
How did you come to know this?

7
00:01:41,910 --> 00:01:43,310
Her Majesty summoned Yu

8
00:01:43,360 --> 00:01:44,440
to Changchun Palace a few days ago

9
00:01:44,440 --> 00:01:45,900
and brought up the matter.

10
00:01:46,000 --> 00:01:47,680
She clearly wanted Yu
to pass the message to you

11
00:01:47,680 --> 00:01:49,080
so you could be prepared.

12
00:01:50,880 --> 00:01:52,539
How do you plan to handle this?

13
00:01:53,640 --> 00:01:56,300
The Empress Dowager's
intentions are obvious.

14
00:01:56,440 --> 00:01:57,720
But she's using the excuse

15
00:01:57,720 --> 00:01:58,880
of securing your family's lineage.

16
00:01:58,880 --> 00:02:00,840
How could you refuse that?

17
00:02:01,280 --> 00:02:03,440
If I want to refuse, I need no reason.

18
00:02:03,760 --> 00:02:05,280
Such a strong rejection

19
00:02:05,280 --> 00:02:07,160
might be seen as disrespecting her goodwill.

20
00:02:07,160 --> 00:02:08,720
Then it becomes your fault.

21
00:02:09,000 --> 00:02:09,800
Absurd.

22
00:02:10,400 --> 00:02:12,120
Everything I do is for the my household,

23
00:02:12,120 --> 00:02:12,960
for His Majesty,

24
00:02:12,960 --> 00:02:14,320
and for the people of this nation.

25
00:02:14,320 --> 00:02:15,800
What fault is there in that?

26
00:02:15,800 --> 00:02:17,720
Your Highness is truly selfless,

27
00:02:17,980 --> 00:02:20,710
sacrificing much
for the country and its people.

28
00:02:21,280 --> 00:02:23,210
But the household is thin in heirs.

29
00:02:23,480 --> 00:02:25,340
If you don't extend the line soon,

30
00:02:25,800 --> 00:02:27,640
how can you nurture someone

31
00:02:27,640 --> 00:02:30,520
as capable as yourself for the court?

32
00:02:34,240 --> 00:02:35,640
Tan, so you already know.

33
00:02:37,720 --> 00:02:38,560
I... I'm fine.

34
00:02:45,440 --> 00:02:47,800
This is Your Highness's regular medicine,

35
00:02:47,800 --> 00:02:49,079
most effective.

36
00:02:50,910 --> 00:02:52,740
These surface wounds

37
00:02:52,760 --> 00:02:55,620
should heal within a few days.

38
00:02:56,010 --> 00:02:56,900
Then you can

39
00:02:57,040 --> 00:02:58,560
once again focus on

40
00:02:58,560 --> 00:03:00,620
your duty to continue the royal line.

41
00:03:04,760 --> 00:03:07,340
Her Highness is so meticulous,

42
00:03:07,740 --> 00:03:10,400
even remembering
His Highness's usual remedy.

43
00:03:12,760 --> 00:03:14,040
The one truly meticulous

44
00:03:14,040 --> 00:03:14,970
is someone else.

45
00:03:15,040 --> 00:03:16,360
How would I know

46
00:03:16,360 --> 00:03:19,079
what His Highness has used for years?

47
00:03:27,300 --> 00:03:30,500
Even a simple gift
from afar carries deep feeling.

48
00:03:30,760 --> 00:03:31,620
Your Highness,

49
00:03:31,720 --> 00:03:34,180
please don't let that sentiment go to waste.

50
00:03:43,860 --> 00:03:45,650
When Her Highness
heard Your Highness were hurt,

51
00:03:45,650 --> 00:03:46,970
she was frantic.

52
00:03:46,990 --> 00:03:48,420
She rushed here right away.

53
00:03:48,420 --> 00:03:49,960
This is what deep affection
between husband and wife

54
00:03:49,960 --> 00:03:50,360
is...

55
00:03:51,400 --> 00:03:52,440
Is truly about.

56
00:03:53,300 --> 00:03:55,320
Yes, yes.

57
00:03:55,800 --> 00:03:56,600
I also heard

58
00:03:56,600 --> 00:03:58,550
that the Empress Dowager wants to
choose a concubine for Your Highness.

59
00:03:58,550 --> 00:03:59,910
And I share that view.

60
00:04:00,120 --> 00:04:01,360
While you're recovering

61
00:04:01,360 --> 00:04:02,600
in the residence,

62
00:04:02,800 --> 00:04:04,240
why not let me

63
00:04:04,240 --> 00:04:06,340
carefully select
a few good families for your consideration?

64
00:04:06,340 --> 00:04:08,980
Then you can make the final decision.

65
00:04:12,120 --> 00:04:14,320
The Empress Dowager's intent is clear.

66
00:04:14,360 --> 00:04:16,560
I will deal with it in my own way.

67
00:04:17,120 --> 00:04:19,839
Your Highness will have
to take a concubine eventually.

68
00:04:19,839 --> 00:04:22,120
Rather than let the Empress Dowager
force someone in,

69
00:04:22,120 --> 00:04:23,160
why not choose someone

70
00:04:23,160 --> 00:04:24,440
you actually favor?

71
00:04:24,800 --> 00:04:25,840
Rest assured,

72
00:04:26,010 --> 00:04:27,960
I will choose a young lady

73
00:04:27,960 --> 00:04:29,240
from a good family

74
00:04:29,260 --> 00:04:30,920
with all the right qualities,

75
00:04:31,040 --> 00:04:33,300
preferably someone even better than me.

76
00:04:33,400 --> 00:04:34,720
But to have such a fine girl

77
00:04:34,720 --> 00:04:35,720
as a mere concubine

78
00:04:35,720 --> 00:04:37,040
would be quite the injustice.

79
00:04:37,040 --> 00:04:38,800
Once she bears an heir for Your Highness,

80
00:04:38,800 --> 00:04:40,230
you could petition
to make her the principal wife.

81
00:04:40,230 --> 00:04:42,290
That wouldn't be out of the question.

82
00:04:46,520 --> 00:04:48,240
What do you mean by this, Tan?

83
00:04:59,240 --> 00:05:01,560
Does His Highness's
injury need herbal decoctions?

84
00:05:01,560 --> 00:05:02,560
How long before

85
00:05:02,560 --> 00:05:04,280
he can bathe again?

86
00:05:10,720 --> 00:05:12,520
Take good care of yourself, Your Highness.

87
00:05:12,520 --> 00:05:14,120
I won't disturb you further.

88
00:05:14,440 --> 00:05:16,100
I'll visit again another day.

89
00:05:16,530 --> 00:05:18,660
Second Young Master Shu, please stay.

90
00:05:18,880 --> 00:05:20,160
The medicine's delivered,

91
00:05:20,160 --> 00:05:21,820
so I should be the one to leave.

92
00:05:22,580 --> 00:05:23,540
Your Highness.

93
00:05:23,780 --> 00:05:25,580
I... I'll walk Her Highness out.

94
00:05:27,220 --> 00:05:29,310
Your Highness, slow down.

95
00:05:29,330 --> 00:05:31,130
What's wrong with Her Highness?

96
00:05:31,760 --> 00:05:32,560
Qizhi,

97
00:05:34,120 --> 00:05:35,860
how did you offend her?

98
00:05:35,890 --> 00:05:37,590
I just took a flogging on her behalf.

99
00:05:37,590 --> 00:05:39,450
What more could I have done wrong?

100
00:05:39,760 --> 00:05:41,680
There are things I shouldn't say...

101
00:05:41,680 --> 00:05:42,920
Then don't say them.

102
00:05:46,760 --> 00:05:47,200
I must.

103
00:05:47,720 --> 00:05:48,680
For your sake, Qizhi,

104
00:05:48,680 --> 00:05:50,040
I must.

105
00:05:50,690 --> 00:05:51,680
You must understand:

106
00:05:51,680 --> 00:05:53,320
only with tolerance
can we accommodate others,

107
00:05:53,320 --> 00:05:55,320
and only with depth can we bear weight.

108
00:05:55,320 --> 00:05:56,800
Flowers need rain and dew,

109
00:05:56,800 --> 00:05:58,800
and women need gentleness and care.

110
00:05:58,870 --> 00:05:59,940
If Her Highness is upset,

111
00:05:59,940 --> 00:06:01,500
she has her reasons.

112
00:06:02,320 --> 00:06:03,950
Women often overthink and doubt.

113
00:06:03,950 --> 00:06:05,950
Bad moods are natural.

114
00:06:06,220 --> 00:06:07,530
And if there's blame to go around,

115
00:06:07,530 --> 00:06:09,290
it falls on us men.

116
00:06:09,620 --> 00:06:10,420
Qizhi,

117
00:06:10,480 --> 00:06:12,100
you must learn to be understanding.

118
00:06:12,100 --> 00:06:14,660
Develop a heart vast as Mount Tai,

119
00:06:14,760 --> 00:06:17,090
broad as rivers that accept every stream.

120
00:06:17,680 --> 00:06:19,000
Don't ask for reasons,

121
00:06:19,020 --> 00:06:20,830
don't argue right or wrong.

122
00:06:21,280 --> 00:06:22,960
Just offer a sincere apology.

123
00:06:22,960 --> 00:06:24,360
It'll smooth things over

124
00:06:24,380 --> 00:06:25,710
and dispel any discord.

125
00:06:26,570 --> 00:06:28,150
What nonsense.

126
00:06:28,960 --> 00:06:30,040
You don't even have a woman

127
00:06:30,040 --> 00:06:30,960
close to you.

128
00:06:31,640 --> 00:06:33,240
What right do you have to lecture me?

129
00:06:33,240 --> 00:06:35,300
These were wise words from my father.

130
00:06:35,950 --> 00:06:37,680
That's all I have to say.

131
00:06:37,800 --> 00:06:39,240
Take care of yourself, Qizhi.

132
00:06:39,240 --> 00:06:41,120
I'll visit another time.

133
00:06:42,100 --> 00:06:43,670
Hey, wait...

134
00:06:43,960 --> 00:06:45,159
No need to see me out.

135
00:06:45,159 --> 00:06:46,840
I'm not the one who's injured.

136
00:07:00,240 --> 00:07:02,600
Sir, bear with it.

137
00:08:11,640 --> 00:08:12,440
When did

138
00:08:12,840 --> 00:08:13,680
Prince of Dingbei's Mansion

139
00:08:13,680 --> 00:08:14,610
gain such a girl?

140
00:08:31,450 --> 00:08:32,220
Chai Gui,

141
00:08:32,320 --> 00:08:34,120
take this to His Highness while it's hot.

142
00:08:34,120 --> 00:08:34,919
-Hurry.
-Yes.

143
00:08:35,360 --> 00:08:36,000
Wait.

144
00:08:38,250 --> 00:08:40,610
What's His Highness meal today?

145
00:08:43,490 --> 00:08:44,790
This West River stew,

146
00:08:44,940 --> 00:08:47,660
and this Yunmeng pork,

147
00:08:47,690 --> 00:08:49,480
his favorites.

148
00:08:49,510 --> 00:08:51,320
His Highness is seriously injured.

149
00:08:51,320 --> 00:08:52,720
He should watch his diet.

150
00:08:53,490 --> 00:08:54,650
Heavy meat,

151
00:08:54,680 --> 00:08:56,400
high salt, greasy dishes,

152
00:08:56,420 --> 00:08:58,140
none are good for recovery.

153
00:09:15,640 --> 00:09:16,500
Your Highness,

154
00:09:16,620 --> 00:09:17,970
external wounds

155
00:09:18,040 --> 00:09:20,040
only require avoiding alcohol and spice.

156
00:09:20,040 --> 00:09:21,920
It's not like

157
00:09:21,920 --> 00:09:23,380
he can't touch meat at all.

158
00:09:33,240 --> 00:09:35,370
A balanced diet of meat and vegetables

159
00:09:35,450 --> 00:09:37,330
is best for healing.

160
00:09:38,240 --> 00:09:39,960
I'll prepare a proper meal plan

161
00:09:39,960 --> 00:09:41,600
for the kitchen to follow.

162
00:09:44,040 --> 00:09:46,000
His Highness risked it all,

163
00:09:46,000 --> 00:09:47,720
flying into a rage for Her Highness's sake.

164
00:09:47,720 --> 00:09:48,960
Such love,

165
00:09:48,960 --> 00:09:50,840
even Heaven bears witness.

166
00:09:54,220 --> 00:09:55,750
But still, that thing he did

167
00:09:55,760 --> 00:09:56,800
was too reckless.

168
00:09:56,830 --> 00:09:58,410
Even I couldn't bear to watch.

169
00:09:58,410 --> 00:09:59,680
Still, rest assured, Your Highness,

170
00:09:59,680 --> 00:10:01,440
everyone in the mansion

171
00:10:01,460 --> 00:10:02,880
is on your side.

172
00:10:02,910 --> 00:10:04,120
To us, there is only one true mistress

173
00:10:04,120 --> 00:10:04,760
of this household,

174
00:10:04,760 --> 00:10:06,360
and that's you.

175
00:10:07,880 --> 00:10:08,880
Isn't that right?

176
00:10:13,440 --> 00:10:15,070
You may all go.

177
00:10:46,200 --> 00:10:46,600
Sir,

178
00:10:47,400 --> 00:10:48,330
it's time to eat.

179
00:11:05,440 --> 00:11:08,360
Is the mansion tight on money lately?

180
00:11:09,280 --> 00:11:10,010
Her...

181
00:12:24,440 --> 00:12:25,520
Have Concubine Yun

182
00:12:25,520 --> 00:12:27,480
deliver this to His Highness later.

183
00:12:27,480 --> 00:12:28,520
He's injured.

184
00:12:28,750 --> 00:12:30,430
A calming scent

185
00:12:30,450 --> 00:12:31,730
will help him sleep.

186
00:12:32,120 --> 00:12:33,250
Yes, Your Highness.

187
00:12:34,720 --> 00:12:35,840
I'd say Your Highness

188
00:12:35,840 --> 00:12:37,800
has a sharp tongue but a soft heart.

189
00:12:41,820 --> 00:12:44,020
He did get hurt because of me, after all.

190
00:12:45,380 --> 00:12:47,440
I just don't want to owe him anything.

191
00:12:48,480 --> 00:12:49,280
Yes.

192
00:12:55,040 --> 00:12:55,900
Your Highness,

193
00:12:56,080 --> 00:12:57,280
there are many new trinkets

194
00:12:57,280 --> 00:12:58,560
and ornaments on South Yuhe Street.

195
00:12:58,560 --> 00:12:59,820
Why not go for a stroll?

196
00:13:00,680 --> 00:13:02,490
Getting out and about

197
00:13:02,560 --> 00:13:05,290
is surely better than
moping around the mansion.

198
00:13:08,900 --> 00:13:12,580
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

199
00:13:14,800 --> 00:13:16,930
Your Highness, where are you heading?

200
00:13:17,000 --> 00:13:18,440
Madam Yun, such recklessness and disrespect

201
00:13:18,440 --> 00:13:19,840
is completely improper.

202
00:13:20,520 --> 00:13:22,320
So what if you know martial arts?

203
00:13:22,320 --> 00:13:23,920
Does that make you superior?

204
00:13:24,600 --> 00:13:25,960
Since you've entered
the Prince of Dingbei's Mansion,

205
00:13:25,960 --> 00:13:27,840
you ought to follow
the rules and observe proper conduct.

206
00:13:27,840 --> 00:13:29,370
If you offend Her Highness,

207
00:13:29,400 --> 00:13:31,130
can you bear the consequences?

208
00:13:32,100 --> 00:13:34,290
Enough. Let her be.

209
00:13:37,700 --> 00:13:40,730
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

210
00:13:55,720 --> 00:13:57,480
Madam Yun, how can you
be so ignorant of protocol?

211
00:13:57,480 --> 00:14:00,210
Do you even see
the Her Highness as your superior?

212
00:14:00,250 --> 00:14:02,050
I see no one above Her Highness.

213
00:14:02,150 --> 00:14:03,510
Then are you aware

214
00:14:03,600 --> 00:14:05,160
according to proper customs and etiquette,

215
00:14:05,160 --> 00:14:06,400
a concubine may not

216
00:14:06,440 --> 00:14:07,960
share a carriage

217
00:14:07,960 --> 00:14:09,080
with the Prince and Princess Consort,

218
00:14:09,080 --> 00:14:10,480
unless explicitly permitted.

219
00:14:10,480 --> 00:14:11,240
I'm aware.

220
00:14:12,120 --> 00:14:13,920
And yet you act so brazenly?

221
00:14:14,320 --> 00:14:15,660
This was His Highness's instruction.

222
00:14:15,660 --> 00:14:17,860
He said that if Her Highness goes out,

223
00:14:18,040 --> 00:14:19,720
I must not leave her side.

224
00:14:21,000 --> 00:14:22,730
Is this meant as a show of force,

225
00:14:23,120 --> 00:14:25,780
or are you trying
to force me to acknowledge her?

226
00:14:28,040 --> 00:14:28,800
Well then,

227
00:14:28,800 --> 00:14:30,430
since it's His Highness's command,

228
00:14:30,430 --> 00:14:32,330
let Concubine Yun come along,

229
00:14:32,490 --> 00:14:34,050
so others won't accuse me

230
00:14:34,380 --> 00:14:36,830
of being petty

231
00:14:36,990 --> 00:14:38,990
and unable to tolerate a concubine.

232
00:14:39,930 --> 00:14:42,840
[Prince of Dingbei's Mansion]

233
00:14:55,360 --> 00:14:57,760
Miss, have a look at our fans.

234
00:14:58,340 --> 00:15:00,120
All handcrafted.

235
00:15:07,450 --> 00:15:09,730
This one is elegant and understated.

236
00:15:10,630 --> 00:15:12,630
This one is dignified and graceful.

237
00:15:14,940 --> 00:15:16,490
Each has its own charm.

238
00:15:17,100 --> 00:15:18,300
Which one do you like?

239
00:15:19,590 --> 00:15:20,960
Thank you, Your Highness.

240
00:15:20,960 --> 00:15:23,160
I don't usually use fans.

241
00:15:26,120 --> 00:15:27,880
And there's no reason for the Princess

242
00:15:27,880 --> 00:15:29,410
to buy a fan for a concubine.

243
00:15:36,210 --> 00:15:38,740
How could Madam Yun
be so unaware of her place?

244
00:15:39,040 --> 00:15:41,480
How long does she intend to follow us?

245
00:15:43,120 --> 00:15:44,780
With her tailing us like this,

246
00:15:45,080 --> 00:15:46,760
it just feels off.

247
00:15:47,140 --> 00:15:48,290
What feels off?

248
00:15:49,850 --> 00:15:51,110
I can't quite explain.

249
00:15:52,300 --> 00:15:53,330
In any case,

250
00:15:53,360 --> 00:15:55,890
find an excuse to
send her back to the mansion.

251
00:15:56,090 --> 00:15:57,450
I want some time alone.

252
00:16:07,110 --> 00:16:08,960
You've already shared
Her Highness's carriage,

253
00:16:08,960 --> 00:16:10,560
and followed along this far.

254
00:16:10,640 --> 00:16:13,200
You should return now, Madam Yun.

255
00:16:13,400 --> 00:16:14,400
Her Highness hasn't returned yet.

256
00:16:14,400 --> 00:16:15,840
How could I go ahead of her?

257
00:16:15,840 --> 00:16:17,200
If something happens to her,

258
00:16:17,200 --> 00:16:18,120
what then?

259
00:16:18,400 --> 00:16:20,600
You being here would cause more danger.

260
00:16:20,600 --> 00:16:21,930
What do you mean by that?

261
00:16:22,320 --> 00:16:24,060
Can't you tell, Madam Yun?

262
00:16:24,160 --> 00:16:26,220
Her Highness doesn't want to see you.

263
00:16:27,280 --> 00:16:28,910
Why doesn't

264
00:16:29,080 --> 00:16:30,610
Her Highness want to see me?

