280
00:17:58,270 --> 00:17:59,670
Tan seemed upset today?

281
00:17:59,080 --> 00:18:04,260
♪ Even rooftops remember
each moonlit night ♪

282
00:18:00,360 --> 00:18:00,880
Sir,

283
00:18:01,280 --> 00:18:03,780
I didn't notice any discontent from her.

284
00:18:04,320 --> 00:18:05,440
Just earlier, Her Highness

285
00:18:05,440 --> 00:18:07,160
went to South Yuhe Street

286
00:18:07,320 --> 00:18:08,760
with Madam Yun and Suxin.

287
00:18:09,200 --> 00:18:11,800
They said they were buying trendy trinkets.

288
00:18:16,320 --> 00:18:16,800
Sir.

289
00:18:18,800 --> 00:18:19,800
Is it good?

290
00:18:20,160 --> 00:18:22,040
Plain and tasteless.

291
00:18:24,400 --> 00:18:26,260
Even your meal is worse than mine.

292
00:18:26,560 --> 00:18:29,020
It's just for recovery. Nothing so extreme.

293
00:18:29,960 --> 00:18:31,890
On the battlefield, food is often scarce.

294
00:18:31,890 --> 00:18:33,150
When supplies run dry,

295
00:18:33,190 --> 00:18:34,830
even tree bark must suffice.

296
00:18:35,480 --> 00:18:37,080
Isn't this better than that?

297
00:18:37,890 --> 00:18:39,550
But that was then, this is now.

298
00:18:40,280 --> 00:18:41,880
We have meat and vegetables.

299
00:18:42,200 --> 00:18:43,720
Why compare it to bark?

300
00:18:49,160 --> 00:18:50,120
Go to the west end of the city,

301
00:18:50,120 --> 00:18:51,480
and bring back a roast chicken.

302
00:18:51,480 --> 00:18:52,040
Yes.

303
00:18:54,610 --> 00:18:56,040
Has there been any progress

304
00:18:56,040 --> 00:18:57,160
on Liu Mo's behavior?

305
00:18:57,160 --> 00:18:59,820
This man, aside
from court and official duties,

306
00:19:00,000 --> 00:19:01,160
goes nowhere else.

307
00:19:01,720 --> 00:19:02,840
He lives alone

308
00:19:03,160 --> 00:19:04,830
and avoids political networking.

309
00:19:04,830 --> 00:19:06,150
He keeps to himself.

310
00:19:06,960 --> 00:19:07,640
However,

311
00:19:07,950 --> 00:19:09,790
our tail just reported

312
00:19:10,160 --> 00:19:10,920
tonight,

313
00:19:10,920 --> 00:19:13,780
he was spotted
wandering around South Yuhe Street.

314
00:19:15,600 --> 00:19:16,440
Didn't you say

315
00:19:17,080 --> 00:19:18,480
Tan went there too?

316
00:19:19,040 --> 00:19:19,520
Yes.

317
00:19:23,480 --> 00:19:23,920
Sir.

318
00:19:25,640 --> 00:19:26,500
Get me dressed.

319
00:19:33,780 --> 00:19:35,840
I am Liu Mo, Vice Minister of Revenue.

320
00:19:36,040 --> 00:19:36,840
Didn't expect

321
00:19:38,690 --> 00:19:40,420
to run into Your Highness here.

322
00:19:43,720 --> 00:19:44,520
Who is that?

323
00:19:45,510 --> 00:19:46,520
Her Highness didn't seem

324
00:19:46,520 --> 00:19:47,640
to know him.

325
00:19:50,000 --> 00:19:51,330
Her Highness's matters

326
00:19:51,600 --> 00:19:53,460
aren't your concern, Concubine.

327
00:19:54,480 --> 00:19:57,210
We're all part
of the household. It's only right.

328
00:19:57,640 --> 00:19:59,320
Who says that?

329
00:20:03,110 --> 00:20:05,310
Vice Minister Liu. How do you know me?

330
00:20:08,360 --> 00:20:09,220
Your Highness,

331
00:20:10,160 --> 00:20:11,760
have you truly forgotten me?

332
00:20:14,480 --> 00:20:17,480
You've brought this guqin
for repair dozens of times.

333
00:20:17,940 --> 00:20:19,680
It really can't be fixed anymore.

334
00:20:19,680 --> 00:20:21,480
Perhaps it's time to replace it.

335
00:20:22,240 --> 00:20:23,080
Once I pass the Spring Imperial Exam

336
00:20:23,080 --> 00:20:25,280
and receive a salary, I'll buy a new one.

337
00:20:29,520 --> 00:20:30,360
Mr. Fang.

338
00:20:30,710 --> 00:20:32,390
Please continue to care

339
00:20:32,440 --> 00:20:34,280
for my Fourth Miss's guqin personally.

340
00:20:34,280 --> 00:20:35,400
Of course.

341
00:20:36,080 --> 00:20:36,880
As it happens,

342
00:20:36,960 --> 00:20:40,020
Fourth Miss, the one
you ordered last time has arrived.

343
00:20:41,260 --> 00:20:42,340
Much appreciated.

344
00:20:47,010 --> 00:20:48,870
This really is a fine instrument.

345
00:20:53,820 --> 00:20:54,540
Sir,

346
00:20:55,480 --> 00:20:56,280
do you have

347
00:20:56,490 --> 00:20:58,420
any used guqin at a lower price?

348
00:20:58,740 --> 00:21:01,240
We only sell new ones here.

349
00:21:01,360 --> 00:21:02,620
But if you're serious,

350
00:21:02,640 --> 00:21:04,000
I'll keep an eye out.

351
00:21:04,420 --> 00:21:06,920
Can't say when one will appear though.

352
00:21:07,520 --> 00:21:08,440
Thank you, sir.

353
00:21:09,200 --> 00:21:09,800
Oh.

354
00:21:10,280 --> 00:21:11,840
If it's not too much trouble,

355
00:21:11,840 --> 00:21:14,700
I could help around the shop,
run errands, odd jobs,

356
00:21:14,720 --> 00:21:16,760
and use the wages
to offset the price of a new guqin.

357
00:21:16,760 --> 00:21:17,920
Would that be acceptable?

358
00:21:17,920 --> 00:21:18,920
Well…

359
00:21:25,760 --> 00:21:28,680
Young Master, might I have the honor

360
00:21:29,450 --> 00:21:30,890
of hearing you play?

361
00:21:32,400 --> 00:21:34,240
I'm afraid my guqin is too damaged.

362
00:21:34,240 --> 00:21:35,770
You might be disappointed.

363
00:21:36,480 --> 00:21:37,280
Suxin,

364
00:21:38,520 --> 00:21:39,600
fetch my guqin.

365
00:21:48,720 --> 00:21:51,360
Catalpa wood, Fuxi style,

366
00:21:53,560 --> 00:21:54,960
lacquered smooth as oil.

367
00:21:58,440 --> 00:22:00,010
Young Miss, if you don't mind,

368
00:22:00,010 --> 00:22:01,450
I shall humbly perform.

369
00:22:31,970 --> 00:22:33,900
You truly are devoted to the guqin.

370
00:22:35,440 --> 00:22:38,480
How can a guqin lover be without one?

371
00:22:39,530 --> 00:22:42,410
Here, consider this guqin a gift from me,

372
00:22:43,060 --> 00:22:44,660
as a token of shared passion.

373
00:22:46,970 --> 00:22:49,230
To play this guqin is already my fortune.

374
00:22:50,160 --> 00:22:51,280
But I dare not

375
00:22:51,280 --> 00:22:52,880
accept such a generous gift.

376
00:22:53,040 --> 00:22:54,000
Your kindness

377
00:22:54,120 --> 00:22:55,440
will stay with me.

378
00:22:56,010 --> 00:22:56,690
Farewell.

379
00:22:58,600 --> 00:23:00,130
Young Master. Please wait.

380
00:23:00,920 --> 00:23:02,830
My lady has a new guqin now.

381
00:23:02,860 --> 00:23:04,560
This old one

382
00:23:04,560 --> 00:23:06,600
will only collect dust on the shelf.

383
00:23:06,760 --> 00:23:08,400
Please take it,

384
00:23:08,420 --> 00:23:09,480
treat it with care.

385
00:23:09,720 --> 00:23:12,380
Let it be your memento
of this melody you shared.

386
00:23:15,790 --> 00:23:17,810
[Marquis of Jing'an's Mansion]

387
00:23:22,920 --> 00:23:25,240
To hear one's music is to know their heart,

388
00:23:25,240 --> 00:23:27,040
and to resonate with each chord.

389
00:23:27,170 --> 00:23:28,530
That one song just now

390
00:23:28,720 --> 00:23:31,360
proves you have the talent of Bo Ya.

391
00:23:32,480 --> 00:23:34,340
May you one day, like the legends,

392
00:23:34,520 --> 00:23:36,160
pluck strings like pines

393
00:23:37,160 --> 00:23:39,090
in mountain winds, or silence them

394
00:23:39,770 --> 00:23:42,030
more powerful than rain on Tai Mountain.

395
00:23:45,550 --> 00:23:47,440
One should not
receive reward without merit.

396
00:23:47,440 --> 00:23:48,000
I cannot

397
00:23:48,000 --> 00:23:49,520
accept such a gift lightly, Young Miss.

398
00:23:49,520 --> 00:23:51,120
Earlier, hearing your tune

399
00:23:51,680 --> 00:23:54,410
was like witnessing
all the beauty under heaven.

400
00:23:54,590 --> 00:23:56,250
Exchanging a guqin for a song,

401
00:23:57,160 --> 00:23:58,890
clearly, I got the better deal.

402
00:24:37,120 --> 00:24:39,450
To hear one's music is to know their heart,

403
00:24:39,520 --> 00:24:41,320
and to resonate with each chord.

404
00:24:42,840 --> 00:24:43,760
Miss Ming,

405
00:24:44,620 --> 00:24:45,320
surely you know

406
00:24:45,320 --> 00:24:47,180
the second half of that poem goes:

407
00:24:47,980 --> 00:24:49,980
“Cease lamenting Heaven's melody,

408
00:24:50,720 --> 00:24:51,440
let it join

409
00:24:53,160 --> 00:24:54,490
our hearts in harmony.”

410
00:24:56,720 --> 00:24:58,320
That was never my intention.

411
00:24:58,960 --> 00:25:00,020
Vice Minister Liu,

412
00:25:00,320 --> 00:25:02,520
you're stretching the meaning too far.

413
00:25:02,560 --> 00:25:03,840
The gift of the guqin back then

414
00:25:03,840 --> 00:25:05,500
was a gesture of passing fate.

415
00:25:05,850 --> 00:25:06,930
As for that matter,

416
00:25:07,980 --> 00:25:09,860
I've long put it behind me.

417
00:25:11,010 --> 00:25:12,810
To you, it was a passing gesture,

418
00:25:13,440 --> 00:25:15,700
but to me, it's remained unforgettable.

419
00:25:17,080 --> 00:25:18,650
Vice Minister Liu, mind your words.

420
00:25:18,650 --> 00:25:21,300
I am already married,
a woman with a husband,

421
00:25:21,520 --> 00:25:23,820
the Princess Consort of Prince of Dingbei.

422
00:25:23,820 --> 00:25:25,640
The one I entrust my life to

423
00:25:25,930 --> 00:25:28,660
is none other than
my husband, Prince of Dingbei.

424
00:25:30,560 --> 00:25:32,160
I ask you, Vice Minister Liu,

425
00:25:32,240 --> 00:25:34,440
to put an end to these deluded thoughts.

426
00:25:34,690 --> 00:25:35,770
Show some respect.

427
00:25:42,420 --> 00:25:43,660
This scent...

428
00:25:44,300 --> 00:25:46,360
I know I am unworthy of you, Miss Ming.

429
00:25:47,180 --> 00:25:48,070
All I hope

430
00:25:52,170 --> 00:25:54,100
is for your safety and well-being.

431
00:26:15,940 --> 00:26:17,530
We barely know each other.

432
00:26:18,520 --> 00:26:20,120
We're strangers in passing.

433
00:26:21,920 --> 00:26:23,850
Vice Minister Liu, don't you think

434
00:26:24,140 --> 00:26:25,610
these words are

435
00:26:25,630 --> 00:26:27,330
rather presumptuous and inappropriate?

436
00:26:27,330 --> 00:26:29,060
More than just inappropriate.

437
00:26:34,600 --> 00:26:36,730
Vice Minister Liu, what is the meaning

438
00:26:39,410 --> 00:26:41,270
of pestering my Princess Consort?

439
00:26:41,270 --> 00:26:43,670
Your Highness, don't jump to conclusions.

440
00:26:43,780 --> 00:26:45,510
If I am misunderstood, so be it.

441
00:26:46,940 --> 00:26:48,710
But don't wrongly accuse the Princess.

442
00:26:48,710 --> 00:26:50,710
Tan has always been above reproach.

443
00:26:51,670 --> 00:26:53,190
It's others

444
00:26:53,220 --> 00:26:56,250
who may harbor hidden intentions.

445
00:26:56,320 --> 00:26:57,400
Tonight, I...

446
00:26:57,420 --> 00:26:58,300
I don't care

447
00:26:58,330 --> 00:26:59,490
why you're here.

448
00:27:00,100 --> 00:27:01,260
Tan's safety

449
00:27:01,390 --> 00:27:03,220
is the responsibility of the palace guards.

450
00:27:03,220 --> 00:27:04,190
And her future,

451
00:27:04,220 --> 00:27:06,430
will be protected by me alone.

452
00:27:06,960 --> 00:27:08,160
I suggest you

453
00:27:08,680 --> 00:27:09,610
know your place.

454
00:27:48,740 --> 00:27:50,670
Why are you upset today?

455
00:27:52,130 --> 00:27:53,370
You know the answer.

456
00:27:53,750 --> 00:27:55,200
You and Vice Minister Liu

457
00:27:55,840 --> 00:27:57,970
ran into each other by chance earlier?

458
00:28:01,220 --> 00:28:03,020
If you ever see him again,

459
00:28:03,480 --> 00:28:04,810
you'd better avoid him.

460
00:28:08,400 --> 00:28:10,310
Vice Minister Liu and I

461
00:28:10,880 --> 00:28:12,440
knew each other in the past.

462
00:28:13,100 --> 00:28:15,640
A brief encounter and a few words.

463
00:28:15,670 --> 00:28:16,910
It's quite normal.

464
00:28:17,420 --> 00:28:18,600
Why should I avoid him?

465
00:28:18,600 --> 00:28:19,610
From before?

466
00:28:19,770 --> 00:28:20,570
That's right.

467
00:28:21,330 --> 00:28:23,330
I met Vice Minister Liu

468
00:28:23,650 --> 00:28:27,470
five years before I ever

469
00:28:27,500 --> 00:28:28,560
met Your Highness.

470
00:28:34,920 --> 00:28:37,050
Your meeting a man at night in private,

471
00:28:37,270 --> 00:28:38,310
is that proper?

472
00:28:38,800 --> 00:28:40,480
Me, meeting a man in private?

473
00:28:40,720 --> 00:28:42,240
Did you feel it improper

474
00:28:42,240 --> 00:28:43,280
when you met with other women?

475
00:28:43,280 --> 00:28:44,760
Official duties have
piled up in the Capital Garrison.

476
00:28:44,760 --> 00:28:45,960
I work day and night.

477
00:28:45,960 --> 00:28:47,360
How would I have time for secret meetings?

478
00:28:47,360 --> 00:28:48,910
She's already entered your mansion,

479
00:28:48,910 --> 00:28:50,840
and yet you still defend yourself?

480
00:28:53,420 --> 00:28:54,800
Feeling guilty, are you?

481
00:28:54,800 --> 00:28:56,400
Men are all the same.

482
00:28:56,420 --> 00:28:59,020
And you, Jiang Qizhi,
you're the worst of them.

483
00:29:00,170 --> 00:29:02,220
All your promises and vows,

484
00:29:02,410 --> 00:29:04,170
nothing but lies.

485
00:29:07,680 --> 00:29:08,900
So you are angry with me

486
00:29:08,900 --> 00:29:11,650
because of Yun Yi?

487
00:29:12,370 --> 00:29:13,290
Still acting?

488
00:29:13,860 --> 00:29:16,700
You truly are a master of playing dumb.

489
00:29:18,160 --> 00:29:19,040
Lately,

490
00:29:19,290 --> 00:29:20,480
the Empress Dowager, citing the need

491
00:29:20,480 --> 00:29:21,880
for heirs of our mansion,

492
00:29:22,240 --> 00:29:23,480
planned to arrange a concubine for me.

493
00:29:23,480 --> 00:29:26,280
So you just went along with it

494
00:29:26,600 --> 00:29:27,930
and took in a concubine?

495
00:29:29,840 --> 00:29:31,080
Why not go all the way

496
00:29:31,140 --> 00:29:32,280
and bring Fengzhao

497
00:29:32,840 --> 00:29:34,400
into the mansion too?

498
00:29:34,790 --> 00:29:36,040
The Empress Dowager's been trying

499
00:29:36,040 --> 00:29:37,160
to pair you two for ages.

500
00:29:37,160 --> 00:29:38,200
That way,

501
00:29:38,310 --> 00:29:39,810
you could fully enjoy

502
00:29:39,830 --> 00:29:42,540
the blessings of many women.

503
00:29:43,240 --> 00:29:44,760
I don't like a crowded household.

504
00:29:44,760 --> 00:29:46,000
You say that, but...

505
00:29:46,000 --> 00:29:47,660
Yun Yi is a secret guard of Jinyun Guards,

506
00:29:47,660 --> 00:29:49,390
no less skilled than Zhuiying.

507
00:29:50,400 --> 00:29:52,280
Bringing her in as a concubine

508
00:29:52,380 --> 00:29:54,320
was to avoid the Empress Dowager's meddling

509
00:29:54,320 --> 00:29:56,850
while also protecting your safety in secret.

510
00:30:05,000 --> 00:30:05,840
So...

511
00:30:07,470 --> 00:30:08,770
She's not a real concubine?

512
00:30:08,770 --> 00:30:10,230
She's just a secret guard?

513
00:30:13,710 --> 00:30:16,110
And no one thought to tell me?

514
00:30:18,600 --> 00:30:20,260
Why didn't you say so earlier?

515
00:30:20,810 --> 00:30:21,820
You nearly had me

516
00:30:22,190 --> 00:30:23,590
wrongfully suspect you.

517
00:30:24,090 --> 00:30:25,510
Since it's a secret identity,

518
00:30:25,510 --> 00:30:27,040
it couldn't be made public.

519
00:30:27,690 --> 00:30:28,300
Yun Yi is a soldier

520
00:30:28,300 --> 00:30:29,460
who follows orders.

521
00:30:29,930 --> 00:30:31,840
When I told her to pose as a concubine

522
00:30:31,840 --> 00:30:33,150
and keep it from everyone,

523
00:30:33,150 --> 00:30:34,790
she kept the secret with her life.

524
00:30:34,790 --> 00:30:36,100
Everyone?

525
00:30:36,130 --> 00:30:37,350
Even me?

526
00:30:37,920 --> 00:30:40,250
So I spent the whole day upset for nothing?

527
00:30:49,560 --> 00:30:51,490
Why are you looking at me like that?

528
00:30:59,950 --> 00:31:01,480
I thought

529
00:31:02,400 --> 00:31:04,240
you took in a concubine

530
00:31:04,280 --> 00:31:05,400
because you resented me

531
00:31:05,400 --> 00:31:07,200
for what happened with Gao Chen.

532
00:31:07,320 --> 00:31:08,480
When I heard Yun Yi

533
00:31:08,480 --> 00:31:09,900
had been with you for many years,

534
00:31:09,900 --> 00:31:11,900
I was heartbroken for quite a while.

535
00:31:13,760 --> 00:31:14,800
I already told you

536
00:31:15,640 --> 00:31:17,960
I never held that against you.

537
00:31:18,500 --> 00:31:23,570
♪ Your name reflects
within a smiling face ♪

538
00:31:25,710 --> 00:31:30,570
♪ May we hold hands,
and not waste these fleeting years ♪

539
00:31:26,870 --> 00:31:27,500
Whatever.

540
00:31:28,710 --> 00:31:30,530
This misunderstanding

541
00:31:30,740 --> 00:31:32,740
is entirely your fault.

542
00:31:33,450 --> 00:31:35,210
You must make it up to me.

543
00:31:33,600 --> 00:31:40,440
♪ With trailing vines as our song,
mountains and seas stay ever bound ♪

544
00:31:36,680 --> 00:31:37,680
Then tell me,

545
00:31:37,700 --> 00:31:39,230
how shall I make it up to you?

546
00:31:40,700 --> 00:31:42,060
Let me think...

547
00:31:41,960 --> 00:31:45,980
♪ Painting a scroll of passion,
fierce and profound ♪

548
00:31:47,210 --> 00:31:51,290
♪ The vows we made together ♪

549
00:31:51,670 --> 00:31:55,000
♪ I'll never regret guarding you
or being wild with you ♪

550
00:31:51,800 --> 00:31:52,400
Like this?

551
00:31:55,350 --> 00:32:01,290
♪ Because the landscape of fate
always bears your shadow ♪

552
00:31:56,120 --> 00:31:56,720
Or this?

553
00:31:58,090 --> 00:31:58,890
Or perhaps

554
00:32:00,460 --> 00:32:01,300
like this...

555
00:32:02,330 --> 00:32:06,140
♪ I wish to become your birthmark ♪

556
00:32:06,370 --> 00:32:10,520
♪ Let time carve our sincerity ♪

557
00:32:10,920 --> 00:32:12,370
♪ Red threads bind us tightly ♪

558
00:32:12,650 --> 00:32:16,710
♪ This is what happiness looks like ♪

559
00:32:33,100 --> 00:32:37,330
♪ Stars sparkle like our first meeting ♪

560
00:32:40,910 --> 00:32:45,650
♪ Music plays on, unafraid of time ♪

561
00:32:45,010 --> 00:32:46,270
You're injured.

562
00:32:46,290 --> 00:32:48,020
You should restrain yourself.

563
00:32:48,990 --> 00:32:55,350
♪ We've weathered darkness and long nights ♪

564
00:32:52,000 --> 00:32:53,680
You get to be bold,

565
00:32:54,170 --> 00:32:55,700
but I must restrain myself?

566
00:32:56,380 --> 00:33:00,910
♪ I fall for you in this lifetime ♪

567
00:32:57,490 --> 00:32:59,600
You were the one who started it.

568
00:33:00,390 --> 00:33:02,150
Why shame me now?

569
00:33:02,180 --> 00:33:06,140
♪ The vows we made together ♪

570
00:33:05,170 --> 00:33:07,110
Ten, just give it ten days.

571
00:33:06,450 --> 00:33:09,960
♪ I'll never regret guarding you
or being wild with you ♪

572
00:33:07,380 --> 00:33:08,580
I'll be fully

573
00:33:08,870 --> 00:33:10,030
healed soon.

574
00:33:10,220 --> 00:33:16,210
♪ Because the landscape of fate
always bears your shadow ♪

575
00:33:12,960 --> 00:33:15,690
Your Highness,
it's time to change the dressing.

576
00:33:16,680 --> 00:33:20,580
♪ I wish to become your birthmark ♪

577
00:33:20,930 --> 00:33:24,830
♪ Let time carve our sincerity ♪

578
00:33:25,220 --> 00:33:26,890
♪ Red threads bind us tightly ♪

579
00:33:27,170 --> 00:33:31,240
♪ This is what happiness looks like ♪

580
00:34:14,280 --> 00:34:16,060
Tan, why do you show up out of nowhere?

581
00:34:16,060 --> 00:34:19,199
[In-depth Study and Profound Reflection]

582
00:34:16,469 --> 00:34:17,780
You're hurt.

583
00:34:17,830 --> 00:34:19,690
How can just this be enough to eat?

584
00:34:19,760 --> 00:34:21,469
I had the kitchen prepare

585
00:34:21,489 --> 00:34:23,179
some of your

586
00:34:23,330 --> 00:34:25,340
favorite snacks.

587
00:34:28,320 --> 00:34:29,320
And I also made

588
00:34:29,320 --> 00:34:31,190
a bowl of bird's nest porridge just for you.

589
00:34:31,190 --> 00:34:32,389
Drink it while it's hot.

590
00:34:31,469 --> 00:34:34,429
[In-depth Study and Profound Reflection]

591
00:34:37,760 --> 00:34:38,920
I was wrong.

592
00:34:40,520 --> 00:34:42,000
What are you saying?

593
00:34:42,719 --> 00:34:44,880
Offending you only brings me harm.

594
00:34:45,760 --> 00:34:47,159
I shouldn't have let you

595
00:34:47,260 --> 00:34:48,320
misunderstand me.

596
00:34:49,170 --> 00:34:50,870
I didn't expect

597
00:34:51,000 --> 00:34:53,080
someone as beautiful as Yun Yi

598
00:34:53,170 --> 00:34:55,630
would be a secret guard
of the Jinyun Guards.

599
00:34:57,480 --> 00:34:59,080
You're physically delicate.

600
00:34:59,080 --> 00:35:00,840
From now on, it's best to rise earlier.

601
00:35:00,840 --> 00:35:02,040
Once I recover,

602
00:35:02,040 --> 00:35:02,760
you'll join me

603
00:35:02,760 --> 00:35:04,400
at the training grounds
to strengthen your body

604
00:35:04,400 --> 00:35:06,280
and learn some self-defense techniques.

605
00:35:06,280 --> 00:35:07,400
Me?

606
00:35:07,420 --> 00:35:08,450
Why should I train?

607
00:35:08,450 --> 00:35:09,360
What would you like to learn?

608
00:35:09,360 --> 00:35:11,090
I don't want to learn anything.

609
00:35:11,560 --> 00:35:13,400
I could teach you archery.

610
00:35:14,100 --> 00:35:16,320
Or grappling techniques.

611
00:35:16,480 --> 00:35:17,800
Grappling?

612
00:35:19,540 --> 00:35:21,340
Archery requires arm strength.

613
00:35:21,740 --> 00:35:23,420
I'm frail and delicate.

614
00:35:23,470 --> 00:35:25,730
I'm afraid I can't even hold a bow steady.

615
00:35:26,320 --> 00:35:29,080
And grappling takes internal strength.

616
00:35:29,100 --> 00:35:30,930
Since childhood, I couldn't lift

617
00:35:30,930 --> 00:35:31,990
or carry anything.

618
00:35:32,160 --> 00:35:34,220
How would I even have inner strength?

619
00:35:34,600 --> 00:35:36,240
Must I really train?

620
00:35:36,600 --> 00:35:37,730
If I did,

621
00:35:37,760 --> 00:35:38,640
I'd be completely drained.

622
00:35:38,640 --> 00:35:40,040
And once I run out of strength,
I'll need rest,

623
00:35:40,040 --> 00:35:41,160
a good long rest

624
00:35:41,160 --> 00:35:41,980
to recover.

625
00:35:42,010 --> 00:35:43,510
By then, I won't be
able to do anything else.

626
00:35:43,510 --> 00:35:44,320
I don't fight battles,

627
00:35:44,320 --> 00:35:45,320
nor do I go to war.

628
00:35:47,400 --> 00:35:49,080
Husband, please spare me.

629
00:35:52,390 --> 00:35:53,470
I believe

630
00:35:53,490 --> 00:35:54,760
life is short and bitter.

631
00:35:54,760 --> 00:35:56,430
We should live as we please.

632
00:35:56,460 --> 00:35:58,520
That's what makes life worth living.

633
00:35:58,840 --> 00:36:00,040
You're right.

634
00:36:02,360 --> 00:36:03,840
I've arranged to meet Minmin later

635
00:36:03,840 --> 00:36:05,760
to distribute supplies at the relief hall.

636
00:36:05,760 --> 00:36:06,760
I've had Suxin

637
00:36:06,760 --> 00:36:07,760
add extra cushions

638
00:36:07,760 --> 00:36:08,800
to the inner room of Qi'an Hall.

639
00:36:08,800 --> 00:36:09,440
You can return early

640
00:36:09,440 --> 00:36:10,900
and rest there for a while.

641
00:36:11,280 --> 00:36:13,080
I'll be back before nightfall

642
00:36:13,440 --> 00:36:15,000
to dine with you.

643
00:36:15,000 --> 00:36:16,130
Take Yun Yi with you.

644
00:36:16,570 --> 00:36:18,760
There have been many
refugees in the city lately.

645
00:36:18,760 --> 00:36:19,840
You must take care

646
00:36:19,840 --> 00:36:20,800
when going out.

647
00:36:22,810 --> 00:36:24,410
And you too, Xu.

648
00:36:24,480 --> 00:36:26,210
Take care not to get hurt again.

649
00:36:33,110 --> 00:36:34,910
A secret guard of Jinyun Guards?

650
00:36:38,940 --> 00:36:40,360
No wonder that concubine

651
00:36:40,400 --> 00:36:41,490
sticks to you so shamelessly,

652
00:36:41,490 --> 00:36:42,560
following you everywhere,

653
00:36:42,560 --> 00:36:44,590
and you even tolerate her.

654
00:36:44,670 --> 00:36:45,770
Turns out, it was your husband's way

655
00:36:45,770 --> 00:36:46,980
of protecting you.

656
00:36:49,020 --> 00:36:50,160
There are still

657
00:36:50,160 --> 00:36:51,840
good men in this world.

658
00:36:52,100 --> 00:36:52,810
By the way,

659
00:36:52,930 --> 00:36:54,760
how did your blind date go the other day?

660
00:36:54,760 --> 00:36:56,260
So many unexpected things happened lately.

661
00:36:56,260 --> 00:36:57,580
I almost forgot.

662
00:36:59,560 --> 00:37:01,080
That Young Master Zhou

663
00:37:01,400 --> 00:37:02,440
is indeed handsome and well-mannered.

664
00:37:02,440 --> 00:37:03,920
Knowledgeable and courteous.

665
00:37:03,920 --> 00:37:05,440
But he's just a bit...

666
00:37:06,400 --> 00:37:07,320
A bit what?

667
00:37:09,320 --> 00:37:10,720
A bit too much of a bookworm.

668
00:37:10,720 --> 00:37:12,560
Always talking about
filial piety and rituals.

669
00:37:12,560 --> 00:37:13,960
Feels like he's marrying

670
00:37:13,960 --> 00:37:15,680
just for the sake of being married.

671
00:37:15,680 --> 00:37:17,810
Who he marries doesn't seem to matter.

672
00:37:17,960 --> 00:37:19,350
Then what do you think

673
00:37:19,640 --> 00:37:21,120
of Young Lord Zhang?

674
00:37:21,680 --> 00:37:23,480
W–Why bring him up again?

675
00:37:23,560 --> 00:37:24,760
Haven't you noticed

676
00:37:24,920 --> 00:37:25,800
he treats you differently

677
00:37:25,800 --> 00:37:27,380
from everyone else?

678
00:37:27,720 --> 00:37:29,160
Of course he does.

679
00:37:29,190 --> 00:37:31,030
He's polite to everyone else,

680
00:37:31,050 --> 00:37:32,650
but only finds fault with me.

681
00:37:32,750 --> 00:37:33,870
Better to

682
00:37:33,890 --> 00:37:35,370
avoid him from now on.

683
00:37:35,400 --> 00:37:38,680
That's called fate binding foes.

684
00:37:38,990 --> 00:37:40,240
If I can't find a husband,

685
00:37:40,240 --> 00:37:41,350
you'll marry me, right?

686
00:37:41,350 --> 00:37:42,390
I'll marry you.

687
00:37:47,920 --> 00:37:48,800
We have food now.

688
00:37:48,800 --> 00:37:49,730
Here, thank you.

689
00:37:53,000 --> 00:37:53,400
Here.

690
00:37:54,320 --> 00:37:54,840
Take it.

691
00:37:55,640 --> 00:37:56,600
Eat slowly.

692
00:37:56,600 --> 00:37:58,760
So good, Mom!

693
00:37:59,880 --> 00:38:00,680
Go over there.

694
00:38:04,170 --> 00:38:06,130
Come, take your medicine.

695
00:38:07,840 --> 00:38:08,400
Be careful.

696
00:38:08,400 --> 00:38:08,920
Okay.

697
00:38:08,920 --> 00:38:10,000
Mom, you eat too.

698
00:38:10,000 --> 00:38:11,200
I'm fine. Eat slowly.

699
00:38:12,800 --> 00:38:13,360
Here.

700
00:38:13,800 --> 00:38:14,480
Thank you!

701
00:38:20,110 --> 00:38:21,640
Minmin, be careful.

702
00:38:21,640 --> 00:38:22,840
Don't hurt yourself.

703
00:38:24,660 --> 00:38:26,280
No need. I can handle it.

704
00:38:26,280 --> 00:38:27,160
Go help someone else.

705
00:38:27,160 --> 00:38:28,400
Why help someone else?

706
00:38:28,400 --> 00:38:30,060
Of course I'm here to help you!

707
00:38:30,460 --> 00:38:32,120
You're so strange, honestly.

708
00:38:32,120 --> 00:38:33,320
Well...

709
00:38:33,510 --> 00:38:35,160
Minmin, I said I want to help you.

710
00:38:35,160 --> 00:38:36,370
Is that wrong?

711
00:38:36,560 --> 00:38:38,270
L–Let me hold this for you.

712
00:38:38,480 --> 00:38:39,280
No need.

713
00:38:39,280 --> 00:38:39,920
Minmin.

714
00:38:45,880 --> 00:38:47,680
Could I trouble you for another bowl?

715
00:38:47,680 --> 00:38:49,400
Kids! Come get roast chicken!

716
00:38:50,960 --> 00:38:52,280
Want some roast chicken? Come on.

717
00:38:52,280 --> 00:38:53,640
I want some, Miss!

718
00:38:53,640 --> 00:38:54,840
Be careful.

719
00:38:54,920 --> 00:38:55,910
No need to rush.

720
00:38:56,160 --> 00:38:57,300
There's plenty for everyone.

721
00:38:57,300 --> 00:38:58,040
I want a drumstick!

722
00:38:58,040 --> 00:38:58,960
I want another piece!

723
00:38:58,960 --> 00:38:59,640
Me too!

724
00:38:59,640 --> 00:39:01,000
It's been so long since we had meat!

725
00:39:01,000 --> 00:39:02,480
I'll get it!

726
00:39:03,720 --> 00:39:05,360
Easy now. Don't fight.

727
00:39:05,360 --> 00:39:06,720
Everyone will get some.

728
00:39:07,730 --> 00:39:08,660
Drumstick girl!

729
00:39:10,840 --> 00:39:11,640
Who are you?

730
00:39:12,000 --> 00:39:13,410
We met briefly yesterday

731
00:39:13,430 --> 00:39:15,230
at Prince of Dingbei's Mansion.

732
00:39:19,360 --> 00:39:21,200
But I'd never

733
00:39:21,200 --> 00:39:22,240
seen you there before.

734
00:39:22,240 --> 00:39:24,120
Are you new to the mansion?

735
00:39:24,740 --> 00:39:26,410
Are we that familiar?

736
00:39:26,480 --> 00:39:27,760
You don't live at the mansion,

737
00:39:27,760 --> 00:39:30,160
isn't it normal you haven't seen me before?

738
00:39:31,760 --> 00:39:33,650
At present, the number
of registered refugees

739
00:39:33,650 --> 00:39:34,980
is 164.

740
00:39:35,000 --> 00:39:36,700
Each gets 20 qian
worth of porridge and cakes daily,

741
00:39:36,700 --> 00:39:38,160
and two strings of coins
for clothing and bedding.

742
00:39:38,160 --> 00:39:39,620
All the numbers check out.

743
00:39:40,560 --> 00:39:41,720
Clearly, you and your brother

744
00:39:41,720 --> 00:39:43,120
have done your part well.

745
00:39:43,720 --> 00:39:44,740
Your Highness's charity

746
00:39:44,740 --> 00:39:45,810
has given

747
00:39:45,840 --> 00:39:46,770
our people hope.

748
00:39:47,040 --> 00:39:48,800
Of course, we must do our part

749
00:39:48,840 --> 00:39:51,100
and avoid adding unnecessary expenses.

750
00:39:55,440 --> 00:39:55,900
This...

751
00:39:56,670 --> 00:39:57,960
Roof repairs,

752
00:39:57,960 --> 00:39:58,880
medical care,

753
00:39:58,880 --> 00:40:00,200
firewood for various locations,

754
00:40:00,200 --> 00:40:01,260
all require funds.

755
00:40:01,760 --> 00:40:02,690
Take this first.

756
00:40:02,730 --> 00:40:04,730
Record all expenses as they come.

757
00:40:05,150 --> 00:40:06,610
Thank you, Your Highness.

758
00:40:06,650 --> 00:40:08,650
I'll go check on the others up front.

759
00:40:12,330 --> 00:40:13,330
By the way, Yun Yi,

760
00:40:13,830 --> 00:40:15,740
why did you join the Jinyun Guards?

761
00:40:15,740 --> 00:40:17,180
Isn't that job harsh?

762
00:40:18,760 --> 00:40:20,200
It's not harsh.

763
00:40:21,670 --> 00:40:24,200
I was orphaned and helpless since childhood.

764
00:40:25,040 --> 00:40:27,840
I survived thanks to His Highness.

765
00:40:28,160 --> 00:40:29,230
So I swore loyalty

766
00:40:29,250 --> 00:40:31,130
to him for life.

767
00:40:32,140 --> 00:40:33,420
But he told me,

768
00:40:33,760 --> 00:40:35,040
once I entered the mansion,

769
00:40:35,040 --> 00:40:36,570
he'd no longer be my master,

770
00:40:36,640 --> 00:40:37,970
Your Highness would be.

771
00:40:38,520 --> 00:40:39,850
You are your own person.

772
00:40:40,460 --> 00:40:42,020
You don't need a master.

773
00:40:44,760 --> 00:40:47,400
But Suxin and Lyu'e

774
00:40:47,560 --> 00:40:49,440
both see you as theirs.

775
00:40:50,950 --> 00:40:52,590
That's just their duty.

776
00:40:53,410 --> 00:40:54,710
If one day

777
00:40:54,750 --> 00:40:56,610
they find a good future elsewhere

778
00:40:56,790 --> 00:40:57,810
and know

779
00:40:57,980 --> 00:40:59,510
what kind of life they want,

780
00:41:01,360 --> 00:41:02,830
I won't stop them.

781
00:41:02,890 --> 00:41:05,530
As for me, I've got no one.

782
00:41:05,760 --> 00:41:08,160
I'll follow Your Highness wherever you go.

783
00:41:10,860 --> 00:41:14,440
[Capital]

784
00:41:16,720 --> 00:41:17,580
Open the gates!

785
00:41:23,650 --> 00:41:25,200
Marquis of Jing'an
failed in disaster relief!

786
00:41:25,200 --> 00:41:26,560
He's negligent and careless!

787
00:41:26,560 --> 00:41:28,560
He doesn't care if people live or die!

788
00:41:28,560 --> 00:41:30,040
Don't push! Don't run!

789
00:41:32,630 --> 00:41:34,760
We beg His Majesty to deliver justice.

790
00:41:36,760 --> 00:41:37,680
Go report this to the officials.

791
00:41:37,680 --> 00:41:38,040
Yes!

792
00:41:38,480 --> 00:41:39,810
Everyone, come with me!

793
00:41:41,240 --> 00:41:41,840
Xu!

794
00:41:43,490 --> 00:41:46,020
Something's happened to Marquis of Jing'an!

795
00:41:49,090 --> 00:41:50,360
How dare you!

796
00:41:56,880 --> 00:41:57,880
Is this

797
00:41:57,880 --> 00:41:59,940
a charity hall sheltering refugees?

798
00:42:00,490 --> 00:42:02,580
Are you from Lizhou?

799
00:42:02,640 --> 00:42:03,980
Yes, yes, that's right.

800
00:42:04,040 --> 00:42:04,720
Alright.

801
00:42:05,040 --> 00:42:05,840
Everyone, please

802
00:42:05,840 --> 00:42:07,040
head to the tents to rest first.

803
00:42:07,040 --> 00:42:08,300
Once we've finished registering your names,

804
00:42:08,300 --> 00:42:10,020
I'll take you to receive your food.

805
00:42:10,020 --> 00:42:11,000
-Let's go, let's go!
-Quickly!

806
00:42:11,000 --> 00:42:11,480
-This way.

807
00:42:11,480 --> 00:42:12,240
Let's go.

808
00:42:12,360 --> 00:42:13,420
This is wonderful.

809
00:42:14,680 --> 00:42:15,840
There's more if it's not enough!

810
00:42:15,840 --> 00:42:17,040
Eat slowly, eat slowly.

811
00:42:17,040 --> 00:42:17,760
You'll definitely have your fill.

812
00:42:17,760 --> 00:42:18,420
Here you go.

813
00:42:18,600 --> 00:42:20,130
There's more if you need it!

814
00:42:20,320 --> 00:42:21,180
This is for you.

815
00:42:22,570 --> 00:42:23,400
That's better now.

816
00:42:23,400 --> 00:42:24,930
Greetings, Your Highness.

817
00:42:25,040 --> 00:42:25,840
Everyone,

818
00:42:26,310 --> 00:42:28,110
this is the Princess of Dingbei.

819
00:42:29,040 --> 00:42:29,970
This relief hall

820
00:42:30,080 --> 00:42:32,140
was built and funded by Her Highness.

821
00:42:32,720 --> 00:42:34,060
The refugees from Lizhou

822
00:42:34,060 --> 00:42:36,460
were also resettled thanks to her efforts.

823
00:42:37,160 --> 00:42:38,410
Princess of Dingbei.

824
00:42:39,040 --> 00:42:41,500
Isn't she the daughter
of the Marquis of Jing'an?

825
00:42:41,500 --> 00:42:42,560
The daughter of the Marquis of Jing'an?

826
00:42:42,560 --> 00:42:44,280
Thank you, Your Highness!

827
00:42:44,280 --> 00:42:45,400
Thank you, Your Highness!

828
00:42:45,400 --> 00:42:47,000
There's no need for all this.

829
00:42:47,070 --> 00:42:48,830
The Marquis of Jing'an is my father.

830
00:42:48,830 --> 00:42:50,530
He went to Lizhou for disaster relief,

831
00:42:50,530 --> 00:42:51,990
and I couldn't be of much help.

832
00:42:51,990 --> 00:42:54,440
So I'm simply doing
what little I can here in the capital.

833
00:42:54,440 --> 00:42:55,820
If there's anything you need,

834
00:42:55,820 --> 00:42:56,980
just let Jin Er know.

835
00:42:57,720 --> 00:42:58,720
It was the Marquis of Jing'an

836
00:42:58,720 --> 00:43:00,200
who left us homeless!

837
00:43:00,490 --> 00:43:02,130
Relief? He did no such thing!

838
00:43:02,160 --> 00:43:04,080
He brought ruin to the people!

839
00:43:04,100 --> 00:43:04,900
That's right!

840
00:43:05,890 --> 00:43:06,750
How can that be?

841
00:43:06,760 --> 00:43:08,450
My father was sent
to Lizhou by imperial decree.

842
00:43:08,450 --> 00:43:09,760
He would have done everything in his power

843
00:43:09,760 --> 00:43:11,090
